---
title: Seasonal Pea Risotto with balsamic Roasted Cherry Tomatoes and Pea Shoots
description: Risotto really is a dish for all seasons. It brings comfort and warmth in the winter but can also be a great showcase for lighter, more summery flavours. This version pops with sweet peas and is complemented by tangy roast cherry tomatoes. Enjoy!
